    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The mutant has little or no resistance to disease, so infection becomes a major threat. This defect only matters if disease-causing agents exist in the campaign. A dirty wound might turn septic, the scratch of a predator might infect, or a common cold might become pneumonia. Such illnesses can inflict up to 10 points of damage per day and are very difficult to cure.</p>"
